"rating":"4.0",
"reviewcomment":"If it&#39;s one those days when you are craving a burger, then come here! If you also starving and REALLY need a burger, then no joke, just get here. Some of the first things I noticed were silverware that was readily available on the counter... which confused me, because they&#39;re burgers... completely makes sense once you see what you order. <br><br>MarienBurger was so good and the staff is friendly. It&#39;s a small joint, so taking it to-go is okay too. I ordered the MarienBurger (partially b/c I can&#39;t read German, so picking this burger that has the same name as the place seemed like a good idea). I had to pick my jaw up when I saw how big it was (which was pointless, since I had to stretch my mouth back open to eat this juicy beast). It has 2 HEARTY patties and your regular fixings on a burger, plus bacon. The burger itself was probably  at least 3.5 inches tall - I don&#39;t understand how people can eat this with a side of fries... Make sure to wipe your hands with the packaged wet napkins they supply!",
