"reviewcomment":"When you feel like spoiling yourself with a good drink (And good dinner) I guess this is one of the places you should end up at.<br>I was asking friends about this place  - some say it&#39;s wonderful and the others say it&#39;s horrible - I LOVED it.<br>We arrived a bit before sunset, the door is being opened for a you, a lady takes away your jacket and you go inside the external elevator that takes you upstairs - impressing.<br>Once we went in I&#39;ve seen dishes that were served that just look super awesome - but this time we came to check the bar, so upstairs friends! <br>The bar looks very trendy, we got one of those cool swinging sofas and just watched the sunset disappear (nice views!) while having a well stirred drink. The variety is quite amazing.<br>Two things - get ready to pay, quite a lot above the usual normal prices (9 euros and up for a cocktail) <br>Dress fancier - this place is not for the casuals - I felt really uncomfortable, next time :)",
